NAME
    App::relpath - Return the relative pathname

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.03 of App::relpath (from Perl
    distribution App-relpath), released on 2014-12-05.

SYNOPSIS
    See the command-line script relpath.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/App-relpath>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-App-relpath>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=App-relpath>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

